{"tid":722132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大獎！ 3戰預測全中章魚哥　已遭漁夫肢解出貨","createTime":"2018-06-29T08:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T10:09:14.000Z","uid":72009,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2a59f7ded6acc3998c4e173fd289ac38a40b9012","tid":722132,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"據《每日新聞》報導，日本北海道小平町盛產巨型章魚，51歲漁夫阿部喜三男，為了讓大家知道當地特產，所以從19日起讓章魚拉比歐預測日本隊戰績，並成功預測「贏」哥倫比亞、「平」塞內加爾、「輸」波蘭。而3戰預測全中的機率僅有27分之1。<br />\n不過正當日本民眾想知道，章魚哥怎麼預測日本隊16強的勝敗時，阿部說今天早上已經將拉比歐肢解準備出貨了「之前全部猜中，讓日本隊突破小組賽真的很高興」，並且說會再抓一隻新的章魚來預測，「第二隻拉比歐也會全猜中的」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.sports.appledaily.com/realtime/20180629/1382114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.sports.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180629%2F1382114&d=Zp%2FOZbqkgEy4%2Bn%2FMoifyyDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=96ddbcd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.sports.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180629%2F1382114&h=c33e4827\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.sports.appledaily.com/realtime/20180629/1382114</a><br />\n<br />\n估中以為唔駛死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340153271e61450eec1beca4056a9f5c5f556166","tid":722132,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"估中左 都要烹"},{"pid":"95e2c8aebb567b49f468451e28644b0ecccfe896","tid":722132,"uid":75969,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"估中都要死<br />\n慘撚過化骨龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea4e76440eb3997654912a5ca01b6cedcb9d639","tid":722132,"uid":183302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"95e2c8aebb567b49f468451e28644b0ecccfe896","tid":722132,"uid":75969,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"估中都要死<br />\n慘撚過化骨龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:41:37.00